{"id": 1163, "genre": 1001, "title": "你旅游的时候都是怎么败家的？", "description": "好不容易抢到三千块的往返机票，最后却一共花掉八万？！（题图来自：Ale Giorgini）", "record_count": 2717, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201608101736584rPhjaVEJWlzopIy.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-13T17:00:04Z", "options": [{"id": 107520, "content": "出来受罪，坐车难受，油钱，吃住，特别是吃，景区贵，外面吃会被宰", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686529}, {"id": 107776, "content": "一天吃四五次饭 无数次甜点 因为走路好累不能亏待自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685819}, {"id": 109056, "content": "也不总玩，也不总吃，也不总来，也不总。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724242}, {"id": 107521, "content": "出门在外，对自己好一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490949}, {"id": 107780, "content": "信用卡好像刷了不用还款一样！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713728}, {"id": 107525, "content": "感觉愉悦就行了，与钱多少无关。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704319}, {"id": 107781, "content": "出来玩就不要考虑减肥了不是吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475133}, {"id": 107782, "content": "感覺這地方不會再來第二次", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408949}, {"id": 107527, "content": "买了纪念品最后还忘了送出去...", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714027}, {"id": 107783, "content": "我就进来看看，并没有发言权", "image": "img/option/option/20160815010831RhJtfHwSdo7N1yGW.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715542}, {"id": 107784, "content": "我就进来看看，并没有发言权", "image": "img/option/option/20160815010932EIKbRZ5nYsT1NqPJ.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715542}, {"id": 107529, "content": "花钱没了平时的顾虑，回去一度以为丢钱了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714600}, {"id": 107785, "content": "卧槽！这个好便宜！这个是最新款！#刷刷刷”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313545}, {"id": 107530, "content": "但那种内心感受不是用钱能买来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710521}, {"id": 107786, "content": "我多的都花了，还给不起这点小钱么???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685081}, {"id": 107531, "content": "都来了 不玩玩 不买点东西怪可惜的", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689839}, {"id": 107787, "content": "花了，回来了，后悔了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715607}, {"id": 107789, "content": "一进店感觉什么都差，盘算好一年的护肤品预算后精挑细选，免税店刷卡刷得敲开心，回家之后下月信用卡账单一出整个人都不太好???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 317901}, {"id": 107534, "content": "这个款式国内没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 353113}, {"id": 107790, "content": "被导游可怜巴巴的说服购物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715632}, {"id": 107535, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714624}, {"id": 118543, "content": "出来就是花钱的，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769047}, {"id": 107536, "content": "鬼知道我下次带你再来是什么时候，其实更悲哀的失去就是有钱没时间花。。。嗯！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714636}, {"id": 107793, "content": "反正3000都花了，也不在意那....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681349}, {"id": 107538, "content": "出门旅游为舒心，玩的舒服，住的舒服，吃的到位！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690532}, {"id": 107794, "content": "穷家富路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686544}, {"id": 108050, "content": "就玩，不太花钱。走走看看～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642016}, {"id": 107539, "content": "来都来了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714658}, {"id": 107796, "content": "我不饿，可是我的嘴巴很寂寞。看到吃的根本停不下来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715690}, {"id": 107541, "content": "j j j", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714658}, {"id": 107797, "content": "穷家富路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715697}, {"id": 107543, "content": "看见喜欢的就想都没想就买了！买完后，发现压根没用", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673825}, {"id": 107799, "content": "比国内专柜便宜那么多 ！不买？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026074}, {"id": 107800, "content": "来都来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651437}, {"id": 107545, "content": "买买买 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675350}, {"id": 107801, "content": "一定要买点东西留个纪念", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571414}, {"id": 107546, "content": "全程住五星级酒店", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675350}, {"id": 107802, "content": "一辈子也来不了几次，抓紧买呀！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710379}, {"id": 107547, "content": "不是我们败家了、是现在的游游景点儿、都收费、能要你五块的决不要四块九、玩儿就给钱、不玩儿就走、原生态已经没有了、", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714683}, {"id": 107803, "content": "我简直捡到大便宜了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529057}, {"id": 107548, "content": "不知道钱去哪里了，就是不知道去哪里了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714689}, {"id": 107804, "content": "买点这个，吃的，这个吃的一口扔，那个拍个照不好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691633}, {"id": 107549, "content": "下次再来都不知道上什么时候了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714702}, {"id": 107806, "content": "老是看见好看的，好吃的，好玩的，就什么都没了，尤其是钱。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709982}, {"id": 107551, "content": "哇，這個卡片盒好漂亮，這個紙製品好漂亮！買買買…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609636}, {"id": 107807, "content": "不买点特产，怎么跟亲戚朋友证（xian）明（bai），这个地方我去过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525614}, {"id": 107808, "content": "开心就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715828}, {"id": 107556, "content": "一口气买了5个gucci，一个LV，一个miu miu……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714718}, {"id": 107558, "content": "既然来了就要尝试这里的特色，要玩的开心嘛，钱什么的都不重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714720}, {"id": 107559, "content": "全花在交通和吃上了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674561}]}